Here’s some Hot Tips from our very own, Jorge, on how to prep the grill for a backyard asada! 🤠

Backyard asadas are core to our Mexican-American culture and one of our favorite ways to gather. In fact, some of our best memories are centered around the grill! Aside from the satisfaction of building a crackling fire and gathering with loved ones around it, a fired-up grill is essential for flavoring and cooking your backyard asada meal. We love that cooking over a fire adds smoke and char to veggies and fajitas. ¡Buen Provecho! ❤️‍🔥
